official_title: A bill to amend the Wild and Scenic Rivers Act to remove the St. Joe River in the State of Idaho from consideration for designation as a wild and scenic river.

summary.text: Removes the Saint Joe River in the State of Idaho from consideration for designation as a wild and scenic river under the Wild and Scenic Rivers Act.
